dc_title_s: Wayne National Forest - Ironton Unit: City of Ironton, Ohio
dc_description_s: These are shapefiles of the Wayne National Forest, by county in Ohio, and of properties owned by the Army Corps of Engineers. The Wayne files show the extent of the land owned by the Wayne in each county. These are compiled directly from the Wayne's own files, except for Athens County (not yet available), and so are subject to the extent of accuracy of their system.
